name: Jamie Strusz
title: Engineering Manager
bio: Jamie leads engineering at FlowFuse, focusing on developer experience, clarity, and building systems and teams that scale.
facts: Builder of high-trust engineering orgs, specializing in turning chaotic systems into scalable ones (and creating themed Slack rituals no one asked for but everyone ends up using)
Loves art history, lifting heavy, and birding; accompanied by Sir Yorick, her certified good boy and distinguished service dog
Chaotic good, and allegedly just three raccoons in a sweater
